{title: Column Layout}
{columns: 2}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Am]Left column [Dm]starts here
[E]First verse on the [Am]left
[Am]Short and sweet and [Dm]clear
[E]Nothing [Am]left
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]Chorus spans the [C]page
[G]Wide and [Am]bold
{end_of_chorus}

{column_break}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[Am]Right column [Dm]begins now
[E]Second verse on the [Am]right
[Am]Balanced layout [Dm]somehow
[E]Looking [Am]tight
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[Am]Still in the [Dm]right column
[E]Third verse flowing [Am]on
[Am]Column break was [Dm]solemn
[E]Nearly [Am]done
{end_of_verse}
